OL,3,CNew vape recycling bins installed in
OL,4,Cthe Scottish Borders to reduce risk
OL,5,Cof battery fires
OL,7,FBins for vapes have been installed at
OL,8,Fevery recycling centre in the
OL,9,FScottish Borders in a bid to reduce
OL,10,Fthe number of fires being caused by
OL,11,Fcrushed batteries.
OL,13,FThe initiative comes after a rise in
OL,14,Fnear-miss incidents where highly
OL,15,Fflammable vapes and e-cigarettes have
OL,16,Fcombusted after being wrongly
OL,17,Fdisposed of in general waste or
OL,18,Fregular recycling bins.
